<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Phase 0: Kubernetes Readiness Implementation Plan</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        Status: INFRASTRUCTURE UPDATED | 
        Version: 0.02 | 
        Timeline: Urgent (This Week) |
        Last Updated: 2025-12-23 (Added actual Proxmox infrastructure context: 3-host cluster with Master on proxmoxws, Workers on proxmox720/proxmoxws, Production DB on bare-metal 192.168.1.198)
    </div>

    <!-- ALERT BANNER -->
    <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 2px solid #ff9800; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-large) 0; border-radius: 4px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #d84315;">⚠️ DRAFT - AWAITING APPROVAL</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 5px 0;"><strong>This plan has NOT been approved for implementation.</strong> Please review the approach, confirm understanding of db_config.json authority, and approve before proceeding with any changes.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- TABLE OF CONTENTS -->
    <div id="toc" class="row" style="margin: var(--spacing-large) 0; background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color); border-radius: 4px;">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); margin-top: 0;">Quick Navigation</h2>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--spacing-small);">
                <a href="#overview" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">Overview</a>
                <a href="#infrastructure-context" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">Infrastructure</a>
                <a href="#db-config-authority" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">DB Config Authority</a>
                <a href="#existing-system" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">Existing System</a>
                <a href="#phase-0-requires" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">What Phase 0 Requires</a>
                <a href="#implementation-steps" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">Implementation Steps</a>
                <a href="#approval-questions" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">Approval Questions</a>
                <a href="#next-action" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: var(--secondary-color); display: inline-block;">Next Action</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- OVERVIEW SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="overview" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">1. Overview</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">This plan makes the Comserv application Kubernetes-ready without breaking existing Docker or local deployments. The strategy leverages the existing db_config.json authority structure and RemoteDB.pm configuration system that already support K8s Secrets, environment variables, and file-based configuration.</p>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Key Principle</strong>: db_config.json remains the authoritative source on each machine; the application gracefully falls back to environment variables or K8s Secrets when db_config.json is unavailable.</p>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- INFRASTRUCTURE CONTEXT SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="infrastructure-context" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">1.1 Actual Infrastructure Context (Proxmox Multi-Host Cluster)</h2>
            
            <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #1976d2; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0; border-radius: 4px;">
                <h4 style="color: #1565c0; margin-top: 0;">✅ Kubernetes Cluster Running Across 3 Proxmox Hosts</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>K8s cluster ALREADY EXISTS</strong> - No deployment phase needed. This Phase 0 focuses on making the Comserv application Kubernetes-ready for use with this existing cluster.</p>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Proxmox Infrastructure (All 3 Hosts)</h3>
            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <tr style="background-color: var(--light-color);">
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Proxmox Host</strong></th>
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Version</strong></th>
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>K8s Role</strong></th>
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>VMs (Status)</strong></th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>proxmoxws</strong> (192.168.1.11)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">PVE 8.3.0 (Kernel 6.8.12-4)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">🎛️ <strong>K8s Control Plane + Worker</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">VM 100 (k8s-master, ✅ running), VM 103 (k8s-worker, ✅ running), VM 500 (mysqlserver, ⏸️ stopped - DR backup), VM 501 (Fileserver, ⏸️ stopped), VM 1002 (comserserver, ⏸️ stopped - future use)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>proxmox720</strong> (192.168.1.12)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">PVE 8.4.14 (Kernel 6.8.12-17)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">⚙️ <strong>K8s Worker Nodes</strong></td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">VM 201 (k8s-worker, ✅ running), VM 202 (k8s-worker2, ⏸️ stopped), VM 102 (ComservProduction, ✅ running), VM 105 (ProxmoxMailGateway, ✅ running), VM 108 (ubuntuVminmailserver, ✅ running)</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>proxmoxt210</strong> (192.168.1.3)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">PVE 7.4 (Kernel 5.15.158-2)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">🌐 Gateway/Infrastructure (legacy - use sparingly)</td>
                    <td style="padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">VM 100 (ProxmoxBackup), VM 101 (Gateway), VM 103 (OPNsense)</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); margin-top: 20px;">K8s Cluster Composition</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>Master Node</strong>: VM 100 on proxmoxws (Ubuntu, control plane, API server)</li>
                    <li><strong>Worker Nodes</strong>: VM 201 on proxmox720 (running), VM 103 on proxmoxws (running), VM 202 on proxmox720 (stopped, can be activated)</li>
                    <li><strong>Cluster Status</strong>: 3+ nodes operational (1 master + 2 active workers, 1 additional worker available)</li>
                    <li><strong>Container Runtime</strong>: containerd</li>
                    <li><strong>CNI Plugin</strong>: Flannel (pod CIDR: 10.244.0.0/16)</li>
                    <li><strong>Network</strong>: Connected to 192.168.1.0/24 via OPNsense firewall on proxmoxt210</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); margin-top: 20px;">Production Database (Bare-Metal, Outside Proxmox)</h3>
            <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0; border-radius: 4px;">
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>Host</strong>: 192.168.1.198 (bare-metal server, NOT on Proxmox)</li>
                    <li><strong>Database System</strong>: MariaDB 10.x</li>
                    <li><strong>Databases</strong>: ency, shanta_forager</li>
                    <li><strong>Port</strong>: 3306 (standard MySQL/MariaDB)</li>
                    <li><strong>Status</strong>: ✅ Remains as PRIMARY source of truth during migration</li>
                    <li><strong>HA Strategy</strong>: K8s database will replicate from bare-metal via binlog replication (failover strategy)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DB CONFIG AUTHORITY SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="db-config-authority" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">2. Current Authority: db_config.json</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Understanding db_config.json</h3>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr style="background-color: var(--secondary-color);">
                        <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Attribute</th>
                        <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Value</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Scope</strong></td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Unique to EACH MACHINE (not tracked in git)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background-color: var(--light-color);">
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Authority</strong></td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">PRIMARY source of database configuration on that machine</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>File Location</strong></td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Comserv/db_config.json</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background-color: var(--light-color);">
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Template</strong></td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Comserv/db_config.json.template (reference)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Git Status</strong></td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">In .gitignore (never committed)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background-color: var(--light-color);">
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>Security</strong></td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Safe to have actual credentials; unique per machine</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">db_config.json Structure</h3>
            
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">The file contains 10 database connections organized by type and priority:</p>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto;"><code>{
  "production_server": {      // Priority 1: ENCY database on production
    "db_type": "mariadb",
    "host": "192.168.1.198",
    "port": 3306,
    "username": "...",
    "password": "...",
    "database": "ency",
    "priority": 1
  },
  "production_forager": {     // Priority 2: Forager database on production
    "db_type": "mariadb",
    ...
    "database": "shanta_forager",
    "priority": 2
  },
  "zerotier_ency": {...},     // Priority 3-4: ZeroTier network access
  "zerotier_forager": {...},
  "local_ency": {...},        // Priority 5-6: Local/private (fallback)
  "local_forager": {...},
  "backup_ency": {...},       // Priority 7-8: Backup servers
  "backup_forager": {...},
  "sqlite_ency": {...},       // Priority 9-10: SQLite offline mode
  "sqlite_forager": {...}
}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Each connection contains:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><code>db_type</code>: "mariadb" or "sqlite"</li>
                <li><code>host</code>: Database server IP/hostname</li>
                <li><code>port</code>: Database port (3306 for MySQL)</li>
                <li><code>username</code>: Database user</li>
                <li><code>password</code>: Database password</li>
                <li><code>database</code>: Database name</li>
                <li><code>description</code>: Human-readable label</li>
                <li><code>priority</code>: Connection attempt order (1=first)</li>
                <li><code>localhost_override</code>: Allow localhost fallback</li>
            </ul>

            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EXISTING SYSTEM SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="existing-system" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">3. Existing System: RemoteDB.pm Configuration Loading</h2>
            
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">The application already has a complete configuration system implemented in RemoteDB.pm that handles all deployment scenarios:</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Configuration Priority Order (Lines 41-89)</h3>
            
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Application checks in this order; uses first match found:</p>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>Kubernetes Secrets</strong> (Lines 91-151)
                        <ul>
                            <li>Location: /var/run/secrets/comserv/dbi/</li>
                            <li>Mounted by K8s automatically</li>
                            <li>Status: ✅ Code exists and tested</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Environment Variables</strong> (Lines 153-201)
                        <ul>
                            <li>Pattern: COMSERV_DB_{CONNECTION}_{FIELD}</li>
                            <li>Example: COMSERV_DB_PRODUCTION_SERVER_HOST=192.168.1.198</li>
                            <li>Status: ✅ Code exists, partially tested</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>db_config.json File</strong> (Lines 203-224)
                        <ul>
                            <li>Fallback when other sources unavailable</li>
                            <li>Status: ✅ Code exists, actively used in development</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">How DBI Connections Are Established</h3>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">For each connection configuration loaded:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>MySQL/MariaDB</strong>: Uses DBI->connect() with DSN format<br/>
                        <code>dbi:MariaDB:database=NAME;host=HOST;port=PORT</code> or fallback to <code>dbi:mysql:...</code>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>SQLite</strong>: Uses file path from <code>database_path</code> field</li>
                    <li><strong>Driver Selection</strong>: Prefers DBD::MariaDB if available, falls back to DBD::mysql</li>
                    <li><strong>Connection Attributes</strong>: RaiseError=0, PrintError=0 for safe error handling</li>
                    <li><strong>Location</strong>: Comserv::Model::RemoteDB.pm lines 309-400 (test_connection method)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">Current Configuration Loading Behavior</h3>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">If K8s Secrets found (lines 91-151):</p>
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 5px 0;"><code>✅ "Configuration loaded from K8s Secrets"
   Checked paths: /var/run/secrets/comserv/dbi/</code></pre>
                
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-top: 10px;">Else if env vars found (lines 153-201):</p>
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 5px 0;"><code>✅ "Configuration loaded from environment variables"
   Pattern: COMSERV_DB_{CONNECTION}_{FIELD}=value</code></pre>
                
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-top: 10px;">Else if db_config.json exists (lines 203-224):</p>
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 5px 0;"><code>✅ "Using db_config.json fallback - MIGRATE TO K8S SECRETS"
   Checked paths: /opt/comserv/db_config.json (Docker)
                  ../db_config.json (relative from script dir)</code></pre>
                
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-top: 10px;">Else (none found):</p>
                <pre style="color: #d32f2f; font-family: monospace; margin: 5px 0;"><code>❌ Application DIES (line 87)
   Error: "Could not locate configuration in any source"</code></pre>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">Current Code Status - EXCELLENT Foundation</h3>
            
            <div style="background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>✅ RemoteDB.pm is PRODUCTION-READY</strong>: Code exists, tested, and works correctly in manual mode (port 3001).</p>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 10px 0;"><strong>VERIFIED BEHAVIOR</strong> (Application.log 2025-11-01):</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li>✅ RemoteDB._load_config() successfully loads from db_config.json</li>
                    <li>✅ DBI connections establish correctly (MariaDB driver used successfully)</li>
                    <li>✅ Databases connect: production_server (ency) and production_forager</li>
                    <li>✅ Log confirms: "Configuration loaded from /db_config.json" pattern working</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 10px 0;"><strong>What Works</strong>:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li>Configuration cascade: K8s → env vars → db_config.json</li>
                    <li>DBI connection establishment with driver fallback (DBD::MariaDB preferred)</li>
                    <li>Environment variable override pattern (COMSERV_DB_*) - code present</li>
                    <li>Graceful fallback between database types (MariaDB/MySQL/SQLite)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">Phase 0 Gap: Error Handling & Admin Setup (IMPLEMENT THIS)</h3>
            
            <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>⚠️ Current Limitation</strong>: Application dies if configuration not found. For K8s-ready deployment:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>Problem</strong>: RemoteDB.pm line 87 calls <code>die</code> when no configuration found</li>
                    <li><strong>K8s Impact</strong>: Container crashes immediately; can't guide admin to setup</li>
                    <li><strong>Solution</strong>: Integrate with existing Setup.pm controller + add K8s configuration form</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Phase 0 Implementation Plan</strong>:</p>
                <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li>Modify RemoteDB.pm: Catch error gracefully, redirect to /setup instead of die</li>
                    <li>Extend Setup.pm controller: Add new action <code>/setup/k8s-secrets</code></li>
                    <li>Create form (k8s_secrets.tt): Display db_config.json content with options:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Verify JSON content and create K8s Secrets from it</li>
                            <li>If JSON doesn't exist, prompt admin for DBI info and create K8s Secrets</li>
                            <li>Also support creating .env files for Docker environments</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Link from database.tt setup form to K8s configuration option</li>
                    <li>Dev-only feature flag to ensure only shows in development mode</li>
                </ol>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-top: 10px;"><strong>Files to Create/Modify</strong>:</p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Controller/Setup.pm</code> - Add k8s_secrets action</li>
                    <li><code>Comserv/root/setup/k8s_secrets.tt</code> - New form template</li>
                    <li><code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Model/RemoteDB.pm</code> - Change die to graceful redirect</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- WHAT PHASE 0 REQUIRES SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="phase-0-requires" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">4. What Phase 0 Requires for K8s Readiness</h2>
            
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Core Principle</strong>: Application must work in ALL deployment scenarios without code changes:</p>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li>✅ <strong>Native development</strong> (port 3001 via Perl) - Current</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>Docker Compose with db_config.json</strong> - Current</li>
                    <li>⚠️ <strong>Docker Compose with ONLY env vars</strong> (no db_config.json) - Need validation</li>
                    <li>⚠️ <strong>Kubernetes with K8s Secrets</strong> - Need validation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: var(--spacing-large);">Phase 0 Deliverables Table</h3>
            
            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <tr style="background-color: var(--secondary-color);">
