                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);">Needed</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>1. Security</strong>: No hardcoded credentials in repo</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #d32f2f;">❌ docker-compose.dev.yml has defaults (lines 18, 23)</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #4caf50;">✅ Remove password defaults, require .env</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: var(--light-color);">
