                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #ff9800;">⚠️ RemoteDB.pm code exists, not fully tested</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #4caf50;">✅ Verify K8s Secrets, env vars, db_config.json</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>3. Network Diagnostics</strong>: Early connectivity detection</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #d32f2f;">❌ docker-entrypoint.sh has no pre-flight checks</td>
