                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #ff9800;">⚠️ Supervisor handles signals, unclear if Catalyst graceful</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #4caf50;">✅ Verify signal handlers, document behavior</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-color);"><strong>5. Health Checks</strong>: Readiness/liveness probes for K8s</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: #ff9800;">⚠️ /health endpoint exists but untested</td>
