                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li>Review Comserv.pm for signal handlers</li>
                    <li>Review supervisor config in docker-entrypoint.sh</li>
                    <li>Test: Send SIGTERM to container, verify clean shutdown</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Approval needed?</strong> NO - just verification</p>
            </div>

            <h3 id="step-6" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large); margin-top: 15px;">STEP 6: Verify Health Check Endpoints (15 minutes)</h3>
            
